#. <section class="sutta" id="sn51.17"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.17:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.17:0.2"
msgid "2. Pāsādakampanavagga"
msgstr "2. Shaking the Stilt Longhouse"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 17. Dutiyasamaṇabrāhmaṇasutta → iddhividhasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn51.17:0.3"
msgid "17. Dutiyasamaṇabrāhmaṇasutta"
msgstr "17. Ascetics and Brahmins (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: abhijjamāne → abhijjamānā (pts1, mr)
#. VAR: parimasiṃsu → parāmasiṃsu (bj, s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "sn51.17:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā anekavihitaṃ "
"iddhividhaṃ paccanubhosuṃ—ekopi hutvā bahudhā ahesuṃ, bahudhāpi hutvā eko "
"ahesuṃ; āvibhāvaṃ, tirobhāvaṃ; tirokuṭṭaṃ tiropākāraṃ tiropabbataṃ "
"asajjamānā agamaṃsu, seyyathāpi ākāse; pathaviyāpi ummujjanimujjaṃ akaṃsu, "
"seyyathāpi udake; udakepi abhijjamāne agamaṃsu, seyyathāpi pathaviyaṃ; "
"ākāsepi pallaṅkena kamiṃsu, seyyathāpi pakkhī sakuṇo; imepi candimasūriye "
"evaṃmahiddhike evaṃmahānubhāve pāṇinā parimasiṃsu parimajjiṃsu; yāva "
"brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vattesuṃ, "
msgstr "“Mendicants, all the ascetics and brahmins in the past,"

msgctxt "sn51.17:1.2"
msgid "sabbe te catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.275"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.17:2.1"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā anekavihitaṃ "
"iddhividhaṃ paccanubhossanti—ekopi hutvā bahudhā bhavissanti, bahudhāpi "
"hutvā eko bhavissanti; āvibhāvaṃ, tirobhāvaṃ; tirokuṭṭaṃ tiropākāraṃ "
"tiropabbataṃ asajjamānā gamissanti, seyyathāpi ākāse; pathaviyāpi "
"ummujjanimujjaṃ karissanti, seyyathāpi udake; udakepi abhijjamāne "
"gamissanti, seyyathāpi pathaviyaṃ; ākāsepi pallaṅkena kamissanti, seyyathāpi "
"pakkhī sakuṇo; imepi candimasūriye evaṃmahiddhike evaṃmahānubhāve pāṇinā "
"parimasissanti parimajjissanti; yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vattissanti, "
msgstr "future,"

msgctxt "sn51.17:2.2"
msgid "sabbe te catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: parimasanti → parāmasanti (bj, s1-3, km) | parimasissanti (pts1)
msgctxt "sn51.17:3.1"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā anekavihitaṃ "
"iddhividhaṃ paccanubhonti—ekopi hutvā bahudhā honti, bahudhāpi hutvā eko "
"honti; āvibhāvaṃ, tirobhāvaṃ; tirokuṭṭaṃ tiropākāraṃ tiropabbataṃ asajjamānā "
"gacchanti, seyyathāpi ākāse; pathaviyāpi ummujjanimujjaṃ karonti, seyyathāpi "
"udake; udakepi abhijjamāne gacchanti, seyyathāpi pathaviyaṃ; ākāsepi "
"pallaṅkena kamanti, seyyathāpi pakkhī sakuṇo; imepi candimasūriye "
"evaṃmahiddhike evaṃmahānubhāve pāṇinā parimasanti parimajjanti; yāva "
"brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vattenti, "
msgstr ""
"or present who wield the various kinds of psychic power—multiplying "
"themselves and becoming one again; appearing and disappearing; going "
"unimpeded through a wall, a rampart, or a mountain as if through space; "
"diving in and out of the earth as if it were water; walking on water as if "
"it were earth; flying cross-legged through the sky like a bird; touching and "
"stroking with the hand the sun and moon, so mighty and powerful; controlling "
"their body as far as the Brahmā realm—"

msgctxt "sn51.17:3.2"
msgid "sabbe te catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattāti."
msgstr "do so by developing and cultivating the four bases of psychic power."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.17:4.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn51.17:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ "
"iddhipādaṃ bhāveti, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion "
"due to enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "sn51.17:4.3"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr "energy …"

msgctxt "sn51.17:4.4"
msgid "cittasamādhi …"
msgstr "mental development …"

msgctxt "sn51.17:4.5"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort."

msgctxt "sn51.17:4.6"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā anekavihitaṃ "
"iddhividhaṃ paccanubhosuṃ—ekopi hutvā bahudhā ahesuṃ … pe … yāva "
"brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vattesuṃ, "
msgstr "Mendicants, all the ascetics and brahmins in the past,"

msgctxt "sn51.17:4.7"
msgid "sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.17:5.1"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, anāgatamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā anekavihitaṃ "
"iddhividhaṃ paccanubhossanti—ekopi hutvā bahudhā bhavissanti … pe … yāva "
"brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vattissanti, "
msgstr "future,"

msgctxt "sn51.17:5.2"
msgid "sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.17:6.1"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, etarahi samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā anekavihitaṃ "
"iddhividhaṃ paccanubhonti—ekopi hutvā bahudhā honti … pe … yāva brahmalokāpi "
"kāyena vasaṃ vattenti, "
msgstr ""
"or present who wield the many kinds of psychic power—multiplying themselves "
"and becoming one again … controlling their body as far as the Brahmā realm—"

msgctxt "sn51.17:6.2"
msgid "sabbe te imesaṃyeva catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā”ti."
msgstr "do so by developing and cultivating these four bases of psychic power.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.17:6.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
